+
+	// When version is a GitHub Actions expression (${{ ... }}), we use an env var
+	// to pass the value safely, preventing shell injection. The env var is set to
+	// the expression which is evaluated by the Actions runtime before the shell runs.
+	// For literal versions, the value is still safe to inline directly.
